and essentially in real time.

00:01:20.230 --> 00:01:23.630
And so it takes the real boring
videos that everyone

00:01:23.630 --> 00:01:29.410
knows and do nothing with and
turns it to unforgettable

00:01:29.410 --> 00:01:31.530
movies that you want to
share with everyone.

00:01:31.530 --> 00:01:36.020
And it does it in a
matter of minutes.

00:01:36.020 --> 00:01:42.495
This seemingly simple task of
editing videos is actually a

00:01:42.495 --> 00:01:48.580
very, very complicated task
involving a lot of artificial

00:01:48.580 --> 00:01:52.010
intelligence technology that is
about understanding what's

00:01:52.010 --> 00:01:55.510
going on inside the video and
then deciding how to tell a

00:01:55.510 --> 00:02:01.190
story out of the footage that
you have, and then doing,

00:02:01.190 --> 00:02:04.450
obviously, all the technical
stuff of delivering the video

00:02:04.450 --> 00:02:07.010
and providing it to the user.

00:02:07.010 --> 00:02:12.330
We founded the company in 2009,
basically just starting

00:02:12.330 --> 00:02:17.430
with very strong technologies
for video understanding, which

00:02:17.430 --> 00:02:20.860
is the domain of, I'd say,
artificial intelligence in

00:02:20.860 --> 00:02:22.550
this video.

00:02:22.550 --> 00:02:28.290
