It doesn't tag the videos.

00:14:13.350 --> 00:14:14.680
It's just raw footage.

00:14:14.680 --> 00:14:17.560
So we need to decide
it automatically.

00:14:17.560 --> 00:14:23.520
And then what we also do is we
take the user selection, for

00:14:23.520 --> 00:14:26.630
instance, the user's selection
of music and theme, and we use

00:14:26.630 --> 00:14:30.530
the selection in order to decide
how to tell the story.

00:14:30.530 --> 00:14:34.450
So, for instance, you can take
basic footage of essentially

00:14:34.450 --> 00:14:39.720
everything and tell it like a
horror story, or tell it like

00:14:39.720 --> 00:14:41.240
a comedy, or tell
it like it's a

00:14:41.240 --> 00:14:44.120
nostalgic, sentimental story.

00:14:44.120 --> 00:14:45.220
And that's editing.

00:14:45.220 --> 00:14:47.990
Editing is manipulation of the
footage, and it can tell a

00:14:47.990 --> 00:14:48.650
